<p class=3D"wp-block-paragraph">where <strong>v</strong><em>=E1=B5=A2</em> =
is the <em>i</em>-th column of <em>V</em>. Place these vectors as columns i=
n the matrix <em>U</em>.</p>
<p class=3D"wp-block-paragraph">If <em>n</em> &lt; <em>m</em> or <em>A</em>=
