<p class=3D"wp-block-paragraph">The <strong>null space</strong> of <em>A=E1=
=B5=97</em>, denoted <em>N</em>(<em>A=E1=B5=97</em>), is the __ set of vect=
ors <strong>x</strong> such that _A_=E1=B5=97<strong>x</strong> <strong>=3D=
