><span class=3D"token punctuation">,</span> S<span class=3D"token punctuati=
on">[</span><span class=3D"token punctuation">:</span>k<span class=3D"token=
 punctuation">]</span><span class=3D"token punctuation">)</span>
plt<span class=3D"token punctuation">.</span>xlabel<span class=3D"token pun=
ctuation">(</span><span class=3D"token string">'Rank of singular value'</sp=
an><span class=3D"token punctuation">)</span>
plt<span class=3D"token punctuation">.</span>ylabel<span class=3D"token pun=
ctuation">(</span><span class=3D"token string">'Magnitude of singular value=
'</span><span class=3D"token punctuation">)</span></code></pre>
<figure class=3D"wp-block-image size-large"><img data-dominant-color=3D"f9f=
